title: 367. Andy & DJ CTI: Federal Judge Sides With Trump, Biden Has Fun With Jay Leno's Cars & Antifa Stands Guard Outside Drag Show
itunes:title: 367. Andy & DJ CTI: Federal Judge Sides With Trump, Biden Has Fun With Jay Leno's Cars & Antifa Stands Guard Outside Drag Show
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss a federal judge siding with Trump announcing her preliminary intent to appoint a special master to review the documents seized by the FBI from Mar-a-Lago earlier this month, President Biden spending time with Jay Leno on the anniversary of the Kabul bombing, and heavily armed Antifa militants standing guard outside a drag show in Texas.
